strings.name: OpenStreetMap Wyoming
strings.description: Mappers and OpenStreetMap users in the state of Wyoming
strings.extendedDescription: OpenStreetMap (OSM) Wyoming is a local collaboration of people interested in contributing their efforts to create free maps. We encourage all of our mappers to organize or suggest mapping events throughout the state. Meetup activities can be simple social mixers, OSM basic to advanced training, or community mapping parties.
